Name: Average time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants that include reviewer assignment delays
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed compared to the elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average waiting time to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed after Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants where Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs subsequently
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded'

Name: Cycle Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed measured from Manuscript Export Succeeded to the next non-system activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Minimum time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-AE Assign Reviewers across all process variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the first occurrence of any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to be followed by Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in standard versus extended variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Reviewer Agreed in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-EIC Accept in successful submission trajectories
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Total resolution time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in cases that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'total'}"
